Install
-------

* Install the applet

sudo cp kw_applet.py copy /usr/local/bin/
sudo chmod 755   /usr/local/bin/kw_applet.py

* configure the applet
sudo cp kw_applet.server/usr/lib/bonobo/servers

* Add the applet to the panel the usual way



Dependences
-----------
python-gtk2
python-gnomeapplet
python-notify


